<html>
<head>
	<title></title>
</head>
<body>
	<div id="header">
		<table width=100% height=100%>
			<tr>
				<td width=20 align="right">
				</td>
				<td width=50%>
					<a href='/users/<%=@user.id%>'>Hello, <%=@user.fname%></a>

				
				</td>
				<td width=0% align="right">
					
				<form action="/session/destroy" method="POST">
			        <input name="authenticity_token" value="<%= form_authenticity_token() %>" type="hidden">
			        <input type="hidden" name="_method" value="DELETE" />
			        <button>Log Out</button>
			    </form>

				</td>
				<td width=20 align="right">
				</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
	</div>

	<div id='howItWorks'>
		<center>
			<h1>How It Works</h1>
				<div id='text'>
					<p>Choose a level and click 'play'.  An image will be loaded, but you will only be able to see a small portion around your cursor, like shining a flash light into a dark room.  Once you find Waldo, click on him to reveal the entire image, signifying the end of the game! </p>
				</div>
		</center>
	</div>

	<div id='chooseLevel'>
		<center>
			<h1>Choose a level!</h1>
				<form action="/match/new" method="POST">
				<input name="authenticity_token" value="<%= form_authenticity_token() %>" type="hidden">
					<select name="level">
						<option selected>Choose a Level</option>
						<option value="easy">Easy</option>
						<option value="intermediate">Intermediate</option>
						<option value="difficult">Difficult</option>
					</select>
				<h1>Hint</h1>
					<div id='text'>
						<p>Hint is a feature you can turn on or off, depending on whether you want to challenge yourself or not. As you get closer to Waldo's secret location, the color of the spotlight ring will gradate towards a 'warmer' color. By default, this feature is turned off.</p>
							<input type="checkbox" name="hint" value="hint">Hint On<br><br>
					</div>
				<h1>Customize Spotlight Size</h1>
					<div id='text'>
						<p>If you're looking to challenge yourself, you can customize the size of the 'spotlight'. We recommend you experiment with this feature after you've gotten the hang of finding Waldo with the given spotlight size.</p>
					</div>
					<button>Play!</button>

				</form>
		</center>
	</div>
</body>
</html>